perl-Test-PerlTidy:
perl-Test-PerlTidy: Runs perltidy on files and reports errors if any of the files differ
perl-Test-PerlTidy: after having been tidied. Does not permanently modify the files being
perl-Test-PerlTidy: tested. By default, perltidy will be run on files under the current
perl-Test-PerlTidy: directory and its subdirectories with extensions
perl-Test-PerlTidy: matching: .pm .pl .PL .t
perl-Test-PerlTidy:
perl-Test-PerlTidy: Homepage: https://metacpan.org/pod/Test::PerlTidy
